XData.name: UrlMap
XData.Data: <Routes> <Route Url="/prc/all" Method="GET" Call="emr.physician.Service:getAll"/> <Route Url="/prc/:id" Method="GET" Call="emr.physician.Service:getPhy"/> <Route Url="/prc/add" Method="POST" Call="emr.physician.Service:addPhy"/> <Route Url="/prc/upd/:id" Method="PUT" Call="emr.physician.Service:updPhy"/> <Route Url="/prc/del/:id" Method="DELETE" Call="emr.physician.Service:delPhy"/> </Routes>
